Text:
Thank you! The original was sufficient but I really appreciate that you synched this up and re-released. It's kind of a pain having two VLCs open at the same time and having to pause them separately.

=)
Windows Media Player and Convert X to DVD do not recognize this file. There is something wrong with the codec. :(
I'm pretty sure I encoded it with xvid so I would make sure you have the right codec installed.
